1) main.f
Control the workflow of the KPROJ program.

2) mod_comp.f
Store the basic units and precision parameters.

3) mod_input
Read the input parameters by a user-friendly control like VASP.

4) mod_wave
Switch interfaces (VASP, QE, Ab-init) based on the filename of wavefunction, and read parameters such as NKPTS, NBANDS, and ISPIN.

5) mod_lattice.f
set up lattice quantities, matrices and calculate G-vectors based on the energy cutoff.

6) mod_fft.f
Fourier transform module.

7) mod_kproj.f
k-projection based on the plane wave method.

8) mod_step_funciton.f
Calculate step function during layer k-projection.

9) merge_bndfiles.f
Merge multiple bs_projected.dat files.


